0underrepresented%20populations%20to%20careers%20in%20the%20construction%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDan%20talked%20about%20how%20we%20need%20to%20envision%20a%20future%20for%20ourselves%20and%20the%20opportunities%20that%20the%20construction%20industry%20could%20provide.%20As%20I%20heard%20Dan%20speak%2C%20I%20thought%2C%20%3Cem%3EHow%20do%20I%20want%20to%20live%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20looked%20at%20Dan's%20confidence%20when%20he%20walked%20into%20the%20room%20demanding%20attention%2C%20how%20he%20carried%20himself%2C%20his%20family%2C%20his%20background%2C%20and%20all%20his%20connections%2C%20and%20I%20was%20convinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d64c1b5-eb35-4b5b-aa2c-8c27ba61784c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20found%20the%20trades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20graduating%20from%20high%20school%20in%20May%202015%2C%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20concrete%20laborer.%20I%20helped%20build%20bridges%2C%20hospitals%2C%20and%20research%20labs%20until%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20spring%202020%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoronavirus-layoffs-furloughs-hospitality-service-travel-unemployment-2020%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20layoff%20due%20to%20COVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20switched%20to%20being%20a%20pipe%20fitter%2C%20first%20as%20a%20laborer%2C%20then%20a%20journeyman%2C%20and%20now%20as%20an%20apprentice%20with%20the%20Local%20562%20Pipe%20Fitters%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20to%20college%20to%20get%20into%20pipe%20fitting.%20You%20go%20to%20a%20training%20center%2C%20which%20is%20like%20a%20two-year%20college%20experience.%20You%20have%20a%20night%20class%20once%20a%20week%2C%20practice%20your%20welding%2C%20study%20blueprints%2C%20math%2C%20and%20OSHA%2C%20and%20they%20pay%20you%20to%20learn.%20Then%2C%20you%20do%20an%20apprenticeship%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22548c12fb-4076-4e61-ac61-f778047db98a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20love%20being%20a%20pipe%20fitter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20gives%20me%20confidence%20knowing%20I%20have%20a%20set%20of%20skills%20that%20are%20needed%20everywhere%20in%20the%20world.%20I%20also%20like%20knowing%20how%20important%20pipe%20fitting%20is%20for%20helping%20all%20businesses%20run%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPipe%20fitting%20isn't%20easy%2C%20and%20not%20everyone%20can%20do%20it%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20a%20lot%20more%20special%20and%20gives%20me%20a%20sense%20of%20accomplishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20three%20takeaways%20I'd%20tell%20anyone%20interested%20in%20entering%20the%20trades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f866a2f-0f6f-4bc5-ab7f-2cc8c44754e8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Know%20your%20why%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20chose%20pipe%20fitting%20or%20construction%2C%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do.%20I%20remember%20my%20cousin%2C%20a%20high-spirited%20plumber%2C%20asked%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20your%20why%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20why%20was%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20help%20my%20mom.%20We%20were%20homeless%2C%20and%20she%20was%20going%20through%20chemotherapy%20for%20breast%20cancer.%20My%20brother%20was%20in%20college%2C%20so%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20her.%20She%20made%20it%20feel%20OK%2C%20so%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20how%20bad%20it%20was%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20I%20know%20I%20never%20want%20to%20be%20homeless%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20someone%20who%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20I%20want%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20ask%20yourself%20why%20you%20want%20it%20and%20then%20figure%20out%20the%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b091ed1c-6ddb-4619-b70a-a3c27fea4281%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20can%20make%20money%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20progression%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20to%20work%20your%20way%20up.%20When%20I%20started%20earning%20good%20money%2C%20making%20%2433%20an%20hour%2C%20I%20got%20laid%20off.%