0centers%20to%20pay%20more%20for%20power.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBig%20Tech%20is%20fighting%20back%20as%20other%20states%20grapple%20with%20how%20to%20charge%20data%20center%20customers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20states%2C%20public%20utilities%20are%20asking%20power-hungry%20data%20centers%20to%20cover%20more%20of%20their%20mounting%20electricity%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUtilities%20have%20long%20enforced%20special%20terms%20and%20conditions%2C%20called%20tariffs%2C%20on%20their%20largest%20customers%2C%20to%20ensure%20they%20are%20paying%20their%20fair%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20historic%20surge%20in%20electricity%20demand%20amid%20Big%20Tech's%20AI%20race%2C%20utilities%20in%20states%20like%20Indiana%20and%20Ohio%20are%20now%20turning%20to%20tariffs%20to%20protect%20residents%20and%20small%20businesses%20from%20higher%20power%20bills%20as%20more%20data%20centers%20come%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20centers%20consumed%20about%204.4%25%20of%20all%20electricity%20in%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Farticles%2Fdoe-releases-new-report-evaluating-increase-electricity-demand-data-centers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy.%20That%20amount%20could%20triple%20by%202028.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20level%20of%20demand%20growth%20hasn't%20been%20seen%20since%20the%201960s%2C%20when%20gains%20in%20efficiency%20tempered%20the%20power%20industry's%20costs%20of%20growth%2C%20protecting%20consumers%20from%20hefty%20rate%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20power%20plants%20are%20more%20expensive%20to%20build%2C%20especially%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Futilities-ai-natural-gas-power-microsoft-meta-amazon-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20gas%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20some%20utilities%20are%20proposing%20to%20serve%20new%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERatepayer%20advocate