ver%20really%20stood%20out%20to%20this%20day.%20The%20person%20was%20applying%20for%20a%20senior%20IT%20systems%20administrator%20job%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20opening%20was%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20bouncing%20boxes%20for%20Uncle%20Sam%202.5%20years%20now%20in%20some%20of%20the%20most%20god-awful%20places%20on%20earth.%20I've%20racked%20servers%20during%20indirect%20fire%2C%20maintained%20contact%20with%20a%20bird%20while%20our%20vehicle%20was%20shot%20up%2C%20mastered%20the%20finer%20art%20of%20the%20many%20uses%20of%20duct%20tape%20and%20how%20it%20applies%20to%20IT%20in%20a%20warzone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20literature%20and%20it%20was%20coming%20from%20a%20techie.%20This%20was%20magic%20right%20out%20of%20the%20gate.%20How%20could%20you%20not%20be%20drawn%20into%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20the%20next%20paragraph%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BI've%20put%20up%20racks%20in%20Namibian%20provinces%20while%20cheetahs%20and%20jackals%20watched%20me%20from%20100%20yards%20away%2C%20I've%20even%20chased%20an%20ostrich%20who%20tried%20to%20steal%20my%20CAT5%20from%20the%20box.%20I've%20worked%20on%20military%20projects%20where%20the%20dotmil%20PM%2Fleadership%20had%20a%20more%20difficult%20time%20making%20decisions%20than%20my%20wife.%20I've%20danced%20in%20the%20Red%20Zone%20with%20Iraqi%20locals%20after%20a%20support%20call%20to%20a%20Forward%20Operating%20Base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20laughing%20now%2C%20and%20reading%20this%20thing%20out%20loud.%20I%20was%20in%20my%20office%2C%20so%20no%20one%20heard%20me.%20I%20come%20to%20the%20best%20part%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BI've%20mastered%20the%20chemistry%20of%20the%20'essential%20caffeine%20stack'%20and%20I%20debunked%20the%20myth%20that%20if%20you%20untie%20your%20belly%20button%2C%20your%20butt%20will%20fall%20off%20(it%20won't!).%20I've%20been%20shot%20at%2C%20shot%20up%2C%20blown%20up%2C%20broken%20and%20put%20back%20together%20again%3B%20from%20Baghdad%20to%20Namibia%20and%20from%20Sudan%20to%20Djibouti.%20I%20strongly%20feel%20that%20I%20have%20the%20skillset%2C%20experience%20and%20thick%20skin%20to%20take%20on%20the%20world%20of%20IT%20in%20the%20greatest%20city%20on%20earth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20called%20the%20guy's%20number%20right%20away.%20I%20didn't%20even%20read%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20It%20turned%20out%20the%20job%20wasn't%20right%20for%20him%2C%20but%20I%20introduced%20him%20to%20the%20founders%20of%20an%20IT%20consulting%20firm%2C%20and%20he%20got%20hired%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%2038%20years%20of%20recruiting%2C%20this%20is%20the%20only%20cover%20letter%20I've%20ever%20responded%20to%20like%20this.%20He%20connected%20the%20role%20to%20his%20experience%20in%20a%20really%20personal%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2203ed4435-baf2-4eec-b5b5-4fc397f99c54%5C%22%3EKnow%20your%20voice%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardest%20thing%20for%20any%20writer%20is%20to%20know%20your%20voice.%20When%20you%20find%20your%20voice%2C%20and%20people%20read%20what%20you%20wrote%2C%20they%20hear%20you.%20They%20don't%20hear%20some%20random%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20putting%20enormous%20faith%20into%20generative%20AI%20to%20help%20us%20write%2C%20but%20whose%20voice%20is%20coming%20out%3F%20You%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsimple-cover-letter-example-unemployed-job-search-never-hear-back-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehave%20to%20find%20yours%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20what%20your%20field%20is.%20Think%20about%20how%20you%20tell%20stories%20to%20your%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20usually%20see%20is%20cookie-cutter.%20Cover%20letters%20all%20start%20with%3A%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Sir%20or%20Madam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3ETo%20Whom%20It%20May%20Concern%3C%2Fem%3E.%20How%20about%2C%20%3Cem%3EDear%20Steve%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20It's%20my%20name.%20I%20like%20my%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20they%20all%20say%20things%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EI've%20noticed%20you're%20seeking%20a%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20your%20skills%20of%20noticing%20a%20job%20listing%20are%20fabulous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20all%20end%20by%20thanking%20you%20for%20reading%20their%20cover%20letter%2C%20like%20I'm%20an%20astronaut%20saving%20humanity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20taking%20the%20time%20to%20consider%20my%20candidacy%20for%20this%20exciting%20opportunity%20at%20your%20esteemed%20organization.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20literally%20black%20out%20when%20I%20read%20lines%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-how-to-write-memorable-cover-letter-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754038441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F688b9a6cf748d8c055f6a4a1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-how-to-write-memorable-cover-letter-2025-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20called%20the%20guy's%20number%20right%20away.%20I%20didn't%20even%20read%20his%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20This%20is%20the%20only%20cover%20letter%20I've%20ever%20responded%20to%20like%20this.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sneedleman%40businessinsider.com%20(Sarah%20E.%20Needleman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecruiter-how-to-write-memorable-cover-letter-2025-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Adani%20Power%20Clocks%2027.1%25%20Sequential%20Surge%20At%20Rs%203%2C305%20Crore%20In%20Q1%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Adani%20Power%20on%20Friday%20reported%20an%20impressive%2027.1%20per%20cent%20sequential%20surge%20in%20the%20April-June%20quarter%20(Q1%20FY26)%20at%20Rs%203%2C305%20crore%20--%20from%20Rs%202%2C599.23%20crore%20posted%20in%20the%20last%20quarter%20(Q4%20FY