very%20day%20except%20on%20Sundays%2C%20the%20Lakers%20player%20fasts%20from%208%3A30%20p.m.%20to%20noon%20the%20following%20day.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20his%20fast%2C%20Don%C4%8Di%C4%87%20heads%20straight%20into%20the%20first%20of%20his%20two%20daily%20workouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20so%20easy%20to%20learn%2C%26quot%3B%20Barrio%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20goal%20of%20fasting%20is%20to%20reduce%20any%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freduce-inflammation-pro-athlete-easy-diet-exercise-tips-nba-allstar-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epost-workout%20inflammation%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Don%C4%8Di%C4%87%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20his%20muscles%20stay%20in%20top%20condition%2C%20Don%C4%8Di%C4%87%20fuels%20up%20with%20250%20grams%20of%20protein%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20sticks%20to%20eggs%20and%20chicken%20during%20meals%20and%20supplements%20with%20shakes%20made%20from%20no-sugar%2C%20low-carb%20whey%20protein%20isolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon%C4%8Di%C4%87's%20nutritionist%2C%20Lucia%20Almendros%2C%20said%20that%20250%20grams%20of%20protein%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20minimum%26quot%3B%20amount%20he%20needs%20to%20eat%20in%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20wants%20more%2C%20he%20can%20eat%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Almendros%20told%20Men's%20Health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20balanced%20diet%20is%20key%3A%20Don%C4%8Di%C4%87%20keeps%20nuts%20on%20hand%20whenever%20he%20needs%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcardiologist-snacks-avoid-better-heart-health-what-to-eat-instead-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enutritious%20snack%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20he%20consumes%20lots%20of%20vegetables.%20He%20also%20often%20has%20fruit%20for%20dessert.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Don%C4%8Di%C4%87%20doesn't%20eat%20gluten%2C%20he%20consumes%20other%20types%20of%20carbs%20like%20rice%20and%20potatoes%20sparingly%2C%20Almendros%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDepending%20on%20the%