man%E2%80%99s%20mission.%20Environmentalist%20Vikrant%20Tongad%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Noida-based%20non-profit%20organisation%20SAFE%20(Social%20Action%20for%20Forest%20and%20Environment)%2C%20decided%20to%20take%20on%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20worked%20on%20a%20similar%20problem%20in%20Ghaziabad%20earlier%2C%20Vikrant%20was%20no%20stranger%20to%20such%20challenges.%20When%20residents%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20help%2C%20he%20visited%20the%20site%20several%20times.%20The%20reality%20was%20grim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20land%20was%20burdened%20with%20waste%20and%20remnants%20of%20illegal%20soil%20mining.%20There%20were%20uneven%20pits%20as%20deep%20as%20six%20to%20eight%20feet.%20The%20air%20hung%20heavy%20with%20toxic%20fumes%20from%20open%20garbage%20burning%2C%20which%20threatened%20the%20health%20of%20nearby%20residents.%20Concerns%20about%20respiratory%20problems%2C%20especially%20among%20asthma%20patients%2C%20were%20rampant%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikrant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20troubled%20the%20local%20community%20most%20was%20the%20potential%20fate%20looming%20over%20their%20heads.%20They%20feared%20this%20site%20could%20turn%20into%20a%20replica%20of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20infamous%20Ghazipur%20landfill%20%E2%80%94%20an%20environmental%20catastrophe%20that%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20mountain%20of%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-3-1753705250-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-477273%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20project%20involved%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%20and%20recycling%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20into%20benches.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20hard%20road%20to%20restoring%2010%20acres%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20verifying%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20problem%20%E2%80%94%20spanning%2010%20acres%20filled%20with%20municipal%20and%20industrial%20waste%20%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20mobilised%20efforts%20through%20his%20non-profit%2C%20SAFE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20this%20herculean%20challenge%2C%20he%20first%20secured%20the%20much-needed%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20from%20the%20Greater%20Noida%20Industrial%20Development%20Authority%20to%20transform%20the%20site.%20His%20strategy%20was%20clear%3A%20involve%20community%20volunteers%2C%20tap%20into%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20funding%2C%20and%20use%20the%20organisational%20strength%20of%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20plan%20was%20meticulous.%20Work%20began%20with%20clearing%2012%20truckloads%20of%20waste%2C%20painstakingly%20shifting%20it%20to%20official%20municipal%20management%20sites.%20Another%201%2C600%20kilograms%20of%20plastic%20waste%20were%20manually%20segregated%2C%20recycled%2C%20and%20even%20used%20creatively%20to%20make%20plastic%20benches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLand%20preparation%20was%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vikrant.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20conducted%20soil%20sampling%20and%20levelled%20the%20land%20to%20fix%20the%20illegal%20mining%20pits%20and%20prepare%20the%20site%20for%20tree%20planting.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20ground%20ready%2C%20saplings%20of%20native%20trees%20like%20peepal%2C%20neem%2C%20and%20banyan%20were%20planted%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F283755%2Fias-officer-hero-converts-dumpyard-miyawaki-forest-plants-trees-abhijit-bangar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20the%20Miyawaki%20method%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Japanese%20technique%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F196850%2Ftamil-nadu-dumpyard-mini-forest-compost-waste-organic-vegetables-chennai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelps%20forests%20grow%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20just%20two%20to%20three%20years%20instead%20of%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20envisioned%20a%20green%20belt.%20To%20keep%20the%20plants%20alive%2C%20we%20hired%20a%20gardener%20and%20installed%20solar%20water%20pumps%20to%20save%20electricity%20while%20watering%20the%20saplings.%20We%20also%20cleaned%20one%20of%20the%20two%20water%20bodies.%20Now%20cleared%20of%20refuse%2C%20the%20pond%20is%20harvesting%20rainwater%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20rains%20arrived%2C%20the%20newly%20planted%20saplings%20thrived%2C%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20once-neglected%20patch%20of%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Fnoida-biodiversity-park-safe-vikrant-tongad-2_11zon-1753705295.jpg%5C%22%20