lage.%20He%20has%20forged%20a%20trail%20in%20seed%20preservation.%20Acknowledging%20his%20expertise%2C%2035%20farmers%20from%20the%20neighbouring%20villages%20flock%20to%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20home%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20and%20insights%20into%20the%20seed%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20sessions%20aren%E2%80%99t%20all%20work%20and%20no%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECookies%2C%20millet%20biscuits%2C%20%3Cem%3Eupma%20%3C%2Fem%3E(porridge%20made%20from%20dry-roasted%20semolina)%2C%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(savoury%20rice%20cake)%2C%20%3Cem%3Eraggi%20laddu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20sweet%20made%20with%20finger%20millet)%20and%20pineapple%20candies%20are%20passed%20around%20the%20group.%20These%20value-added%20products%2C%20Darlapudi%20explains%2C%20are%20sold%20under%20the%20brand%20%E2%80%98Bhaskara%E2%80%99.%20But%20the%20question%20that%20most%20farmers%20insist%20on%20having%20answered%20while%20munching%20on%20the%20healthy%20snacks%2C%20is%20how%20the%20seed%20preservation%20is%20accomplished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECataloguing%20India%E2%80%99s%20food%20past%20through%20a%20seed%20bank%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenges%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331574%2Fmobius-foundation-youth-for-earth-campaign-icse-sustainability-startups-climate-change%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20climate%20change%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20habitat%20destruction%20reduce%20genetic%20diversity.%20This%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20modern%20agriculture%E2%80%99s%20reliance%20on%20monocultures%20and%20high-yield%20varieties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20from%20the%20International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature%20(IUCN)%2C%20more%20than%20one%20in%20three%20tree%20species%20worldwide%20faces%20extinction.%20This%20genetic%20erosion%20is%20wiping%20out%20seed%20varieties%20at%20a%20rapid%20pace.%20And%20seed%20banks%20are%20a%20potential%20antidote%20to%20this%20problem%2C%20preserving%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20plant%20genetics%2C%20and%20providing%20a%20resource%20for%20reintroducing%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Darlapudi%20breaks%20down%20the%20nuances%20of%20seed%20preservation%20to%20his%20audience%20of%20enthusiastic%20farmers%2C%20the%20process%20promises%20intrigue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20Ravi%20is%20preserving%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20when%20planted%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20loaded%20with%20health%20benefits%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Ffabric-business-Tohfa-6-1732015271-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381102%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarlapudi%20Ravi%20is%20preserving%20indigenous%20seeds%20that%20when%20planted%20will%20give%20rise%20to%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20loaded%20with%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20before%20we%20dive%20into%20that%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20understand%20why%20the%20practice%20is%20crucial.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20green%20revolution%20came%20the%20devaluation%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310545%2Fmp-lahari-bai-baiga-tribal-woman-preserves-rare-millets-seed-bank-ambassador-year-of-millets%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etraditional%20and%20native%20seeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20genetic%20modification%20gained%20popularity%2C%20the%20genetically%20improved%20traits%20made%20it%20tough%20for%20the%20seeds%20to%20survive%20in%20adverse%20climatic%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20seeds%20give%20quantity%20but%20not%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darlapudi%20says.%20%E2%80%9CInstead%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(local%20varieties)%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20two%20important%20qualities%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20sustain%20natural%20calamities%20and%20give%20a%C2%A0good%20aroma.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20says%2C%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20hybridised%20varieties.%20The%20first%20step%20of%20seed%20preservation%20is%20seed%20collection.%20%E2%80%9CI%20chose%20tribal%20areas%20that%20do%20not%20get%20much%20water%2C%20aside%20from%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20rainfall.%20This%20creates%20drought-resistant%20seeds.%20I%20collected%20seeds%20from%20the%20Pottangi%20area%20in%20Odisha%2C%20the%20Dantewada%20area%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Seethampeta%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Velur%20in%20Kerala.%20These%20include%20seeds%20of%20medicinal%20value%20and%20paddy%20varieties.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20collection%2C%20Darlapudi%20uses%20a%20varied%20array%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F189462%2Fdebal-deb-seed-bank-conserves-native-rice-variety-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreservation%20methods%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20range%20from%20potting%20the%20seed%20in%20mud%20or%20a%20bamboo%20container%20or%20applying%20soil%20to%20the%20seed%20and%20keeping%20it%20in%20the%20shade.%20But%20one%20of%20his%20favourite%20methods%20is%20coating%20the%20seed%20with%20ash.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20varieties%20like%20pumpkin%20or%20creepers%20come%20with%20slurry%20inside.%20Ash%20from%20burning%20dried%20cow%20dung%20is%20applied%20to%20the%20seeds%20and%20they%20are%20kept%20in%20bamboo%20containers%20or%20mud%20pots.%20This%20ash%20acts%20as%20a%20layer%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20seeds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20The%20seeds%20remain%20viable%20even%20after%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Darlapudi%20has%20preserved%20over%203600%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20belts%20across%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fseed-preservation-Darlapudi-Ravi-1732015410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-381105%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDarlapudi%20has%20preserved%20over%203%2C600%20varieties%20of%20indigenous%20seeds%20from%20tribal%20belts%20across%20India.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seed%20