of%20a%20peacock%E2%80%99s%20feathers%20onto%20the%20surface%20of%20a%20piece%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Indian%20sweet).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20decades%20of%20culinary%20experience%20ensured%20he%20aced%20the%20task.%20And%20now%20for%20replicating%20the%20same%20onto%20a%20hundred-odd%20pieces!%20Known%20to%20push%20the%20envelope%2C%20Khanna%20does%20justice%20to%20this%20reputation%20when%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20each%20feather%20to%20be%20exactly%20alike.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20how%20the%20plumage%20was%20meant%20to%20be%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emandirs%20%3C%2Fem%3E(temples)%20in%20Indian%20homes%2C%20Khanna%20was%20keen%20that%20every%20guest%20at%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20his%20dream%20restaurant%20project%20launched%20in%20New%20York%20in%20March%20this%20year%20%E2%80%94%20return%20home%20that%20day%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288997%2Fpunjabi-wrestler-harbans-vig-invented-indias-loved-dhodha-barfi-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebox%20of%20coconut%20%3Cem%3Ebarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20spot%20the%20delicate%20%3Cem%3Emor%20pankh%3C%2Fem%3E%20(peacock%20feather)%2C%20and%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22vikas%20khanna%20exclusive%20on%20starting%20bungalow%20restaurant%20in%20new%20york%20inspired%20by%20his%20indian%20roots%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-12-1729605875-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371717%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EChef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20created%20%E2%80%98Bungalow%E2%80%99%20in%20New%20York%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20street%20vendors%20of%20India%20and%20the%20food%20he%20grew%20up%20eating%20in%20Amritsar%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20positively%20brimming%20with%20joy%20to%20announce%20the%20%3Cem%3Ebarfis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehad%20the%20desired%20effect%3B%20as%20many%20Indian%20immigrants%20found%20themselves%20transported%20by%20the%20mini%20square-shaped%20time%20capsules%20from%20America%20to%20the%20epicentre%20of%20the%20festive%20madness%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevered%20on%20the%20culinary%20circuit%2C%20Vikas%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20prowess%20transcends%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-hyphenate%20has%20authored%20over%2037%20books%20%E2%80%94%20with%20his%20most%20recent%20%E2%80%98Imaginary%20Rain%E2%80%99%20(2023)%20being%20turned%20into%20a%20Shabana%20Azmi%20starrer%20%E2%80%94%20has%20directed%20three%20films%20and%20two%20documentaries%3B%20been%20one%20of%20the%20judges%20at%20MasterChef%20India%3B%20and%20helmed%20several%20restaurants%20including%20New%20York%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20%E2%80%98Junoon%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20first%20Indian%20restaurants%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F357879%2Fmichelin-star-indian-restaurants-avatara-junoon-gaa-veeraswamy-gymkhana-rania-tamarind-semma-benares%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereceive%20the%20coveted%20Michelin%20star%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20this%20compelling%20bio%2C%20Khanna%E2%80%99s%20primary%20identifier%20is%20that%20of%20a%20proud%20Indian.%20And%20this%20is%20reflected%20in%20everything%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Etadka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spices%20heated%20in%20hot%20oil)%20that%20makes%20its%20way%20into%20his%20curries%20to%20the%20sparkle%20in%20his%20eyes%20when%20he%20speaks%20about%20life%20back%20in%20his%20beloved%20hometown%2C%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFor%20Vikas%20Khanna%2C%20all%20roads%20lead%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhanna%E2%80%99s%20culinary%20mind%20has%20a%20lot%20to%20occupy%20it.%20Memories%20of%20serving%20the%20who%E2%80%99s%20who%20of%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20he%20has%20been%20the%20%3Cem%3Echef%20du%20jour%3C%2Fem%3E%20multiple%20times%20for%20the%20Obama%20family%2C%20while%20also%20working%20closely%20with%20food%20mogul%20Gordon%20Ramsay%20%E2%80%94%20find%20space%20right%20next%20to%20nostalgic%20memories%20of%20binge%20sessions%20involving%20rounds%20of%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20patties)%20from%20%E2%80%98Mathura%20ki%20Tikki%E2%80%99%20in%20Amritsar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Among%20Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna's%20fondest%20memories%20are%20those%20with%20his%20family%20and%20the%20time%20he%20spent%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20his%20hometown%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-1-1729603557-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F