%20%3Cem%3Etikkis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Echaat%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F246397%2Fstreet-food-vendors-pav-bhaji-american-civil-war-cotton-mill-portugese-mumbai-video-ros174%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estreet%20food)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20peace%20without%20500-odd%20people%20thronging%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20their%20favourite%20chef%20or%20(if%20they%E2%80%99re%20lucky)%20a%20selfie.%20And%20Khanna%20is%20ever-obliging%2C%20animatedly%20chatting%20up%20each%20vendor%20he%20visits.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20all%2C%20they%20were%20my%20foundation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20perfectly%20segues%20his%20next%20thought%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20often%20take%20things%20for%20granted%20when%20we%20have%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chef%20Vikas%20Khanna%20treasures%20his%20earliest%20memories%20of%20feasting%20on%20the%20food%20prepared%20by%20his%20grandmother%20and%20mother%20%E2%80%94%20experiences%20that%20he%20will%20remember%20forever%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvikas-khanna-2-1729603673-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-371666%5C%22%2