20Restore%2080%20Dying%20Ponds%20Near%20Delhi%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20sprawling%20urban%20jungle%20of%20Delhi%20NCR%2C%20where%20concrete%20reigns%20and%20water%20bodies%20are%20often%20left%20gasping%20for%20breath%2C%20one%20man%20has%20been%20quietly%20bringing%20ponds%20back%20to%20life.%20Ramveer%20Tanwar%2C%20a%20former%20engineer-turned-ecological%20restorer%2C%20is%20fondly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Pond%20Man%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20a%20title%20earned%20through%20tireless%20efforts%20that%20have%20revived%20over%2020%20wetlands%20in%20and%20around%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20from%20boardrooms%20to%20birdcalls%20is%20not%20just%20about%20ecological%20revival%20but%20about%20restoring%20faith%20in%20community-led%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20BTech%20to%20backwaters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Dadha%20village%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Ramveer%20completed%20his%20BTech%20in%20Mechanical%20Engineering%20in%202014.%20Even%20as%20a%20student%2C%20he%20had%20begun%20to%20notice%20a%20troubling%20pattern%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394956%2Findia-pond-man-ramveer-tanwar-revives-ponds-filled-with-garbage-waste%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20ponds%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20once%20played%20in%20were%20disappearing.%20Once%20teeming%20with%20life%2C%20these%20water%20bodies%20had%20become%20garbage%20pits%2C%20overrun%20with%20weeds%20and%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-30T154545.853-1753870571.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ramveer%20Tanwar%2C%20a%20former%20engineer-turned-ecological%20restorer%2C%20is%20fondly%20known%20as%20the%20%E2