rindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Ffeatured-img-5_11zon-1753884698-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-478547%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECommunity%20meetings%20in%20Bhitarkanika%20give%20families%20a%20platform%20to%20plan%20solutions%20to%20local%20climate%20challenges.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20striking%20outcome%20of%20these%20efforts%20is%20the%20People%E2%80%99s%20Climate%20Atlas%20%E2%80%94%20a%20set%20of%20visual%20maps%20and%20datasets%20tracking%20groundwater%20levels%2C%20rainfall%20changes%2C%20and%20extreme%20weather%20events.%20Built%20using%20community%20surveys%20and%20satellite%20data%2C%20the%20atlas%20helps%20policymakers%20design%20responses%20rooted%20in%20ground%20realities%2C%20not%20assumptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeetings%20that%20bring%20back%20forests%20and%20fields%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bhitarkanika%2C%20conversations%20at%20these%20meetings%20often%20circle%20back%20to%20the%20same%20struggles%3A%20shrinking%20livelihoods%2C%20saltwater%20creeping%20into%20farmlands%2C%20and%20wildlife%20attacks%20that%20are%20becoming%20more%20frequent.%20Erratic%20rainfall%20has%20pushed%20families%20to%20abandon%20paddy%20cultivation%20and%20fishing%2C%20turning%20instead%20to%20prawn%20farming%20%E2%80%94%20even%20though%20it%E2%80%99s%20illegal.%20But%20that%2C%20too%2C%20brings%20heartbreak%2C%20as%20prawn%20mortality%20wipes%20out%20their%20investment%20and%20leaves%20them%20in%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForest%20access%20has%20tightened%20under%20conservation%20laws%2C%20cutting%20people%20off%20from%20essentials%20like%20honey%2C%20crabs%2C%20and%20nalia%20grass