ous%20Ways%20to%20Conserve%20Water%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWater%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20essential%20and%20invaluable%20resources%20of%20nature%2C%20we%20cannot%20live%20without%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20a%20phrase%20that%20in%20one%20form%20or%20another%20we%20all%20have%20heard%20countless%20times.%20We%20are%20also%20aware%20that%20much%20like%20the%20other%20gifts%20of%20nature%2C%20this%20too%20is%20not%20unlimited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20yet%2C%20we%20continue%20to%20struggle%20to%20let%20this%20fact%20percolate%20into%20our%20conscious%20minds.%20From%20the%20waking%20moment%20in%20front%20of%20the%20bathroom%20sink%20where%20the%20tap%20runs%20constantly%20as%20we%20brush%20away%20the%20morning%20blues%2C%20to%20the%20millions%20of%20tonnes%20of%20impurities%20that%20are%20daily%20discarded%20into%20the%20water%20bodies%2C%20our%20actions%20continue%20to%20disregard%20the%20fact%20that%20water%20is%20indeed%20a%20limited%20resource.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOwing%20to%20this%2C%20four%20billion%20people%20across%20the%20globe%2C%20which%20is%20two-thirds%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20continue%20to%20experience%20water%20scarcity%20for%20over%20a%20month%2C%20every%20year.%20According%20to%20UNICEF%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unicef.org%2Fwash%2Fwater-scarcity%23%3A~%3Atext%3DKey%2520facts%2Cby%2520as%2520early%2520as%25202025.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eestimate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20half%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20population%20by%202025%20would%20be%20living%20in%20areas%20facing%20acute%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FE23IxHYVoAEKCoA-1753800077-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rainwater%20harvesting%20map%20of%2