ystem%2C%20valleys%20are%20cut%20into%20terraced%20plots%20separated%20by%200.6%20meters%20high%20earthen%20dams%20that%20are%20supported%20by%20bamboo%20frames.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20these%20plots%20have%20an%20inlet%20and%20outlet%20on%20the%20opposite%20sides.%20Deeper%20channels%20are%20also%20created%20that%20connect%20the%20inlet%20point%20to%20the%20outlet%20point%2C%20so%20that%20the%20terraced%20plots%20can%20be%20flooded%20or%20drained%20off%20with%20water%20simply%20by%20opening%20or%20blocking%20these%20inlets%20and%20outlets%2C%20as%20per%20requirement.%20This%20method%20of%20water%20harvesting%20is%20still%20used%20in%20the%20rural%20parts%20of%20the%20state%2C%20especially%20in%20wet%20rice%20cultivation%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F406762%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-innovative-solutions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efish%20farming.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBaoli%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%20wp-image-280155%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-2-1648034157.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20baolis%20were%20built%20exclusively%20for%20agricultural%20purposes%20and%20had%20a%20robust%20drainage%20system%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-2-1648034157.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-2-1648034157-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-2-1648034157-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-2-1648034157-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F03%2Fwater-