thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FGowtham-Reddy-2-1700051890-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334175%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20terracotta%20planter%20was%20made%20using%2060%20percent%20soil%20and%2040%20percent%20of%20low-weight-expanded%20clay.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20simple%20yet%20fascinating%20college%20experiment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20Gowtham%20decided%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20industrial%20design.%20In%202016%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%2C%20Gujarat.%20Here%2C%20he%20says%2C%20he%20was%20encouraged%20to%20follow%20the%20philosophy%20of%20%E2%80%98learning%20by%20doing%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20his%20semester%20project%2C%20he%20interviewed%20a%20few%20gardeners%20to%20understand%20the%20difficulties%20they%20face%20in%20watering%20plants%20while%20away.%20%E2%80%9CI%20focussed%20on%20designing%20the%20product%20in%20a%20simple%20manner%20while%20ensuring%20that%20the%20functionality%20is%20viable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20the%20engineer%20came%20up%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F178559%2Findia-innovation-low-cost-automatic-watering-system-plants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eself-watering%20%3C%2Fa%3Eterracotta%20planter%2C%20made%20using%2060%20percent%20soil%20and%2040%20percent%20of%20low-weight-expanded%20clay.%20%E2%80%9C